This function MAY throw to revert and reject the transfer. Return of other than the magic value MUST result in the transaction being reverted. Returns `bytes4(keccak256("onERC721Received(address,address,uint256,bytes)"))` unless throwing.

params._from: The address which previously owned the token.
params._tokenId: The NFT identifier which is being transferred.
